<button class="accordion">What are examples of harassment in the workplace?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Here are a few examples of harassment based on data from the 2018 Hiscox workplace harassment study:</p>
<li>Sexual and gender employee harassment</li>
<li>Racial harassment in the workplace</li>
<li>Office harassment related to religious beliefs</li>
